Package: vcfppR
Title: Rapid Manipulation of the VCF/BCF Format in R
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zilong", "Li", , "zilong.dk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5859-2078"))
Description: The vcfpp is an easy-to-use API of htslib, offering the full functionlities as the htslib to manipulate the VCF/BCF. Thus, this package is built upon the vcfpp to provide rapid genomic variant analyses on the VCF/BCF file in R.
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
